quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  23,51,"(Allah vakataura kuti): “Imi vatumwa! Idyai zvakachena, mova munoita mabasa akanaka. Zvirokwazvo, ndinoziva zvikuru zvose zvamunoita.”"
  23,52,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, ichi chitendero chenyu (Islaam) chimwe chete, uye ndini Tenzi venyu. Nokudaro, ivai munonditya.”"
  23,53,"Asi (vanhu) vakave vanopatsanura chitendero chavo pakati pavo mumapoka-poka, boka rimwe nerimwe (boka rose) richifara nezvarinazvo"
  23,54,Saka vasiyei mukurasika kwavo kwekanguva
  23,55,Vanofunga here kuti kuvawedzera muhupfumi nevana
  23,56,Kuti tirikuvapa zvakanaka nekukurumidza? Kwete! (Asi muedzo pasi pano kuti vasave nemugove muhupenyu hwemangwana) asi havazvifungi
  23,57,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotya Tenzi vavo vakangwarira"
  23,58,Uye avo vanotenda muzviratidzo zvaTenzi vavo
  23,59,Uye avo vasingasanganisi Tenzi vavo nechimwe chinhu (mukunamata)
  23,60,"Uye avo vanopa (Swadaqah) zvavanopa moyo yavo izere nokutya (kuti zvatambirwa here kana kuti kwete), nokuti vachave zvirokwazvo vanodzokera kuna Tenzi vavo"
  23,61,"Ndeavo vanomhanyira kumabasa akanaka, uye ndivo vekutanga maari"
  23,62,"Uye hatikomekedzi munhu kusara kweizvo zvaanogona, uye tine gwaro rinotaura chokwadi, uye havave vachatadzirwa"
  23,63,"Asi moyo yavo yakaputirwa kubva kwariri (Qur’aan, kurinzwisisa), uye vane mabasa mamwe (akaipa) kusara kweayo avari kuita"
  23,64,"Kusvika taparadza vapfumi pakati pavo nemurango (vasingatarisiri); tarisai, vanova vanochema neizwi riripamusoro (kuna Allah) vachida rubatsiro"
  23,65,"Musacheme neizwi riripamusoro nhasi! Zvirokwazvo, hamuve munobatsirwa nesu"
  23,66,"Zvirokwazvo, ndima dzangu dzakave dzinoverengwa kwamuri, asi imi maifuratira nezvitsitsinho zvenyu (muchidziramba)"
  23,67,"Muchizvitutumadza, muchitaura usiku zvakashata pamusoro paro (Qur’aan)"
  23,68,"Uye havave here vanodzamisa pfungwa dzavo pamusoro peshoko (raAllah, Qur’aan), kana kuti kwakauya kwavari izvo zvisina kuuya kune madzitateguru avo"
  23,69,"Kana kuti havazivi mutumwa wavo (Muhammad (SAW)), saka vachimuramba"
  23,70,"Kana kuti vanotaura (kuti): “Ane kupenga maari?” Asi akavawunzira chokwadi (Islaam), asi vazhinji vavo (vasingatendi) vanoramba chokwadi"
  23,71,"Asi dai chokwadi chakatevera izvo zvavanoshuvira, zvirokwazvo, matenga uye nepasi uye avo vari mazviri zvaidai zvisina kumira zvakanaka (zvaishata)! Asi tavaunzira yeuchidzo yavo, asi ivo vanofuratira yeuchidzo yavo"
  23,72,"Kana kuti iwe (Muhammad (SAW)) unovabvunza mubairo? Asi mubairo waTenzi vako ndiwo wakanaka, uye ndivo (Tenzi vako) nyanzvi pakupa raramo"
  23,73,"Uye zvirokwazvo, unovakoka (Muhammad (SAW)) kunzira yakatwasuka (Islaam)"
  23,74,"Asi zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi muhupenyu huri mushure mekufa, vari zvirokwazvo kubva munzira yakatwasuka (Islaam)"
  23,75,"Uye nyangwe tikavapa tsitsi uye tobvisa matambudziko ari pavari, vanoramba vachingoita zvitadzo zvavo, vachidzungaira vasingadi (chokwadi, vachiita nokusaziva)"
  23,76,"Uye takave tinovabata nemarwadzo (tinovatumira seyambiro), asi havana kuva vanozvininipisa kuna Tenzi vavo, uye havana kusheedza (Allah) vachizvipira kwavari"
  23,77,"Kusvikira\ttavavhurira\tgonhi\tremarwadzo\tmakuru,\tnenguva\tdiki\tvachange\tvarimo vachishungurudzika"